{"type": "article", "id": 32472, "title": "ZARA 母公司上半年利润大涨，以及，MK 联手 Fujifilm 推相机包 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-22T02:12:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6253, "name": "美国零售业"}, {"id": 12570, "name": "拍立得"}, {"id": 21203, "name": "相机包"}, {"id": 24719, "name": "Yeezy Boost"}, {"id": 33031, "name": "法国女装"}, {"id": 1653, "name": "Michael Kors"}, {"id": 1802, "name": "Zara"}, {"id": 2634, "name": "Under Armour"}, {"id": 7776, "name": "NikeLab"}, {"id": 16147, "name": "Totokaelo"}, {"id": 2433, "name": "Cara Delevingne"}, {"id": 4703, "name": "刘雯"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 61, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160922100658gFQ3HKhalzOZoYkD.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/inditex-profits-zara-sales-grow-10556619/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>西班牙零售巨头 Inditex 上半年净利润大涨 </b></a>| 2016 上半年，Zara 的母公司 Inditex 集团净利润上涨了 7.5%，至 12.6 亿欧元。其中，Zara 和 Zara Home 的销售额分别上涨了 13% 和 17%。&nbsp;</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/totokaelo-founder-jill-wenger-steps-down\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Totokaelo 的创始人 Jill Wenger 将要离职</b></a> | 在前不久，创立于 2008 年的美国轻奢精品店 Totokaelo 被背包品牌 Herschel 收购之后，它的创始人兼首席执行官 Jill Wenger 将要离职。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/government-trade/frances-womens-rtw-sales-decline-2-8-in-h1-10556633/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>法国女式成衣市场 2016 上半年销售达三年来最低点</b></a> | 据法国女装联盟的数据显示，2016 上半年，法国女式成衣市场销售额下降了 2.8%，至 49 亿欧元。发生在法国的恐怖袭击对女装市场造成了较大影响，仅仅是在 2016 年 4 月，女装销售额就暴跌了 8.2%。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/baltimore-oks-finance-deal-for-under-armour-ceos-5-5-billion-project\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>巴尔的摩市批准了 UA 的 CEO Kevin 的地产公司项目</b></a> | 巴尔的摩市通过了关于这个 55 亿美元地产项目的 6.6 亿美元的融资方案。据称，该项目涉及巴尔的摩市的基础设施建设，能够促进就业。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/us-holiday-sales-to-grow-but-big-chains-getting-smaller-piece\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国零售业预计在年底假日季上涨 4%</b></a> | 根据德勤咨询的报告所称，美国零售业预计在 2016 年底的假日季期间业绩上涨 4%。但是，像沃尔玛、梅西百货这样的大型公司的增长率会大大低于其他更加细分的零售商。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>在 Rihanna、Kylie Jenner 和刘雯之后，Cara Delevingne 成为 PUMA 最新的宣传大使。<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/cara-delevingne-puma-ambassador\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cara 出镜的这一组宣传大片名为「DO YOU」</a>，表达一种当代年轻女性无畏、自信的态度。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084207D1ZsdNxYq7jUPpRK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609220842076eu5dFlo0kyWnTcm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084207IQ5o0hyPUOTaRWSw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084208vKSG6b7m8YLMUyI4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084208zyld4eHSuC6KVGET.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084216Pr91omqhG7ObjM24.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084216U8wXaH1bjqFr7EtJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084216GmnYJDRuMgQsU4Pv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/adidas-yeezy-boost-350-v2-oxford-tan\" rel=\"nofollow\">YEEZY BOOST 最新作 350 V2 发布新的 Oxford Tan 配色</a>，仍然采用了第一代的 Tan 色，原来抢眼的橙红色划痕则变成了白色，并带有白色的 SPLY-350 字样，该款具体的发售日期待定。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084133iUgzOLW3DCRGxmS1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084133WOx2dgjoPhtV8mJG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084134Wk8mtHFL4bpB7uvd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084139qNTFpQiKrZcd1s64.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666341\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>刘雯、Liya Kebede、Elisa Sednaoui、Amanda Murphy，众名模携手出镜 <a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/giorgio-armani-fall-2016-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Giorgio Armani 2016 秋冬 New Normal</a> 宣传大片。这组黑白时尚大片由法国摄影师 Peter Lindbergh 掌镜。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609220838287bVNocvxmjg3A19J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922083828w7VKaxktu8ZHmWEe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609220838416flR9zuYOTWr8wtp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609220838475fjG0sYz8yXFqoAE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922083847y5OaoDJ03wlIWExG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922083847CuFDfS5bpYTj2rcW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/michael-kors-fujifilm-instant-film-camera-10555445/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Michael Kors 与 Fujifilm 合作</a>，推出相机包，这也是 Fujifilm 首次与时尚品牌跨界合作，这款相机包将于 10 月 20 日在 Michael Kors 生活方式店正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609220838583HuzZvqjFfTe5b4O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.263538\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609220838581QpLa8dChnzc2fqy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922083909ef8QmNVoKX9abTnH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609220839279o7vK2n0BlYXr8UP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922083932mZoHPj80AQCNwd6U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922083937tCcxISGNfHsE6OuY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">NikeLab 与 Kim Jones 的合作系列 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/nikelab-x-kim-jones-collection-2016-fw/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">Packable Sport Style </a>再推新品，沿用了 Nike Tech Fleece 面料，轻量透气。结合了功能性和时尚性，还挺适合做情侣运动装的。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084748p65X78HjnNDMKFo2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084748YxnMJAtVcslNfQZ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922084748B6WrzNTIGXy4vHpU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}